{"tid":1897570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Tesco向華潤子公司出售中國合資公司20%股權","createTime":"2020-02-25T20:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T02:40:33.000Z","uid":47674,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7fac4f20f60b3dee1d560214dd8ff24f4e7922da","tid":1897570,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T20:06:17.000Z","msg":"英國佬仲話支持一帶一路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那邊有好嘢架 早走早著啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Tesco向華潤子公司出售中國合資公司20%股權</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510699-20200225.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510699-20200225.htm&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=1c0f05ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510699-20200225.htm&h=e59d44d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510699-20200225.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n英國最大零售商Tesco公布，以2.75億英鎊向華潤子公司出售中國合資公司20%股權，退出中國市場。<br />\n<br />\nTesco表示，出售相關股權令公司得以進一步簡化業務，並集中於核心業務營運。所得資金將用作一般企業用途，交易將於本月28日完成。"},{"pid":"ef8143bddf4f0b6331d092240522f78fb38b1882","tid":1897570,"uid":155949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7fac4f20f60b3dee1d560214dd8ff24f4e7922da","tid":1897570,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T20:06:17.000Z","msg":"英國佬仲話支持一帶一路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那邊有好嘢架 早走早著啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Tesco向華潤子公司出售中國合資公司20%股權</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510699-20200225.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510699-20200225.htm&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=1c0f05ad\" data-ef-url=\"http